_______________________________________________________________________________
"Combat Teleport"
        This allows the psionicist to teleport an object he is
        carrying into an enemy, resulting in damage from system
        shock.  The weight of the object, and the skill of the
        psionicist determine the amount of damage inflicted.
        The item that is used in this attack will probably be
        destroyed, but there is a chance that it will survive
        and can be recovered when the target is killed.
        Note:  The psionicist must be in combat with the
        intended target.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  5		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  ctel <object> OR
          tctel <object> at <target>
